  "description": "All Echo frames: frame canvas 40x40px, transparent background. No outlines. No shading. No gradients. No dithering. Colors: body #FFA300, cheek patch #FF004D, crest #FFEC27, beak/feet #AB5236, eyes #1D2B53. Echo occupies approx x=6..33,y=6..36 within the 40x40 canvas. Cheek patch is always present as a 3x3 block at x=24..26,y=18..20. Eyes are two 2x2 blocks at x=14..15,y=16..17 and x=22..23,y=16..17 unless the frame specifies eyes closed. Eating: 6 frames, FPS=4, loop=false (play once). Head movement: frames 1-3 head moves down by +2px in y; frame 4 beak open (replace beak 3x2 triangle with 3x3 open shape); frame 5 includes a #FFA300 seed pixel at x=20,y=24 near beak; frame 6 head returns to normal y.",
